.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
4 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, mah-jongg, bridge
City: new-york, colone, paris, marseilles
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the person traveling to paris is between the owner of the dog and the person traveling to colone##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person traveling to colone##8
 6. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the person traveling to new-york is the owner of the frog##1
10. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person traveling to paris##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
14. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person traveling to colone##8
18. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Game          | bridge     | billiard | backgammon | mah-jongg  |
| City   | colone    | paris  | marseilles | new-york |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

