 3. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the coach##5
 4. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the firefighter##8
 6. the aristoff-smoker is not to the left of the librarian##8
 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the librarian is on the left of the coach##1
 9. the coach is on the left of the architect##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the firefighter is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the coach is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
