 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
10. the fan of blues is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person who likes blood-red##8
12. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
