 9. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
10. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the manager##3
11. the musician is on the right of the freelancer##1
12. the manager is not the pall-mall-smoker##6
13. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
