 3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
 4. the social-worker is the person eating apple##1
 5. the person eating lettuce is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person eating peach and the person eating garlic##7
 7. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
 8. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the person playing scrabble##7
 9. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
10. the librarian is not to the left of the librarian##8
11. the electrician is on the far left##1
12. the videographer is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the trike is the person playing monopoly##1
14. the person playing monopoly is not to the left of the person eating garlic##8
15. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
16. the librarian is not to the left of the person playing chess##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4       |
