The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, chinchilla, lizard, rat
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
12. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Birthday      | december   | august     | october    | june |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Pet     | rabbit     | lizard | rat | chinchilla     |

