The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, bellflower, tulip
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, house, indie, trance
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter, jet-ski, quad-bike
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person who growstulip##8
 3. the person drinking sprite is the fan of house##1
 4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 6. the person who growsbellflower is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 9. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person who growstulip##8
10. the fan of indie is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
11. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of trance is not to the right of the person who growstulip##8
14. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
