 6. the person driving the van is the person eating peach##1
 7. the polish is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 8. the mexican is on the far right##1
 9. the turkish is not to the right of the person eating pomegranate##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the polish##8

