.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, social-worker, teacher
City: boston, marseilles, nizza, colone
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, tea, coffee
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the bartender##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 3. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 4. the teacher is the person traveling to colone##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the social-worker##6
 6. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the social-worker##8
 8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
10. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
11. the person traveling to boston is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the social-worker and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| Job           | bartender | doctor    | social-worker | teacher    |
| City   | nizza   | boston | marseilles     | colone    |
| Beverage   | sprite   | tea      | fanta         | coffee     |

 